{"tid":342400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★柒出國際！劏房相集吸引National Geographic深入採訪 !!","createTime":"2017-07-31T14:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T11:35:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61f4ccaf98008edba17f369ef1fb844d112f7696","tid":342400,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://gameover.com.hk/?p=350079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgameover.com.hk%2F%3Fp%3D350079&d=7xwA1LCTBZptFpxobPm7rkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=76eeabd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://gameover.com.hk/?p=350079</a><br />\n<br />\n作為香港人，睇到呢啲相應該好感觸，仲有啲憤怒。成日聽人講籠屋、劏房，但實際環境有幾惡劣？香港攝影師Benny Lam呢輯相令市民睇得深入啲，仲吸引到外國嘅《National Geographic》採訪。攝影師自己都話影完返到屋企忍唔住喊咗出嚟。用咗4年時間走訪超過100間舊居劏房，屋內尺寸由15尺去到120尺，睇完記得follow埋佢嘅facebook page「SOCO Trapped 侷住」，可以留言發聲、參加簽名運動、攝影比賽或者做義工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/31095120/758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F31095120%2F758.jpg&h=0f0b8152&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aeeeffbbe4e3c7ccd39ae2dda472a3e0e6d78c5","tid":342400,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.stream4free.top/images/playerbackground/natgeowild.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.stream4free.top%2Fimages%2Fplayerbackground%2Fnatgeowild.jpg&h=8e5fa7c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed5ee9c7c09fe349405ce5b635038a389de881e7","tid":342400,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KJj6nYfMZUs/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FKJj6nYfMZUs%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=42c2a99b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f07bf41a5a95bc536dfb9823669951393f059aa4","tid":342400,"uid":33477,"like":2,"disl